caller_intent: Follow-up on a received voicemail to request specific information about vehicle plate submission and removal.
resolution_steps: Agent left a voicemail message requesting the date the plate was turned in and details about the vehicle to be removed.
Offered to send a text message for clarification.
Provided a callback phone number for further assistance.
knowledge_required: Understanding of vehicle insurance claim processes
summary: This is a voicemail follow-up from Alliance Insurance agent Jason, requesting specific details about a vehicle plate submission and removal process. The agent offered to send a text message and provided a callback number for further assistance.
